tests.title: should verify that the page can be reset after category selection
tests.fullTitle: Cart interactions should verify that the page can be reset after category selection
tests.code:
cy.get(_products.default.categorySelect).select('laptop'); // selects the laptop option in the category field
cy.get(_homePage.default.mackBookProTitle).should('have.text', 'Mackbook Pro'); //verifies that a laptop product has been returned
cy.get(_homePage.default.resetBtn).click(); // resets the filtering that was done
cy.get(_homePage.default.fittedHatTitle).should('have.text', 'Quality Fitted Hat'); // verifies that the reset was succesful
